# 🚀 Space Game BV 👾

A small space shooter game I made while learning Pygame 😄

This was just a fun personal project using my friends' images because normal enemies are boring.

I mostly made this to learn game development with Python and mess around with Pygame.

---

## 🎮 Features

- Simple arcade-style gameplay
- Funny custom character images
- Keyboard controls
- Made with Python + Pygame

---

## 📦 Installation

### 1. Clone the repository

```bash
git clone <your-github-repo-link>
cd <repo-name>
```

### 2. Install requirements

```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

### 3. Run the game

```bash
python "space game BV.py"
```

---

## 🕹️ Controls

| Action | Key |
|---|---|
| Move Left | `J` |
| Move Right | `L` |
| Move Down | `K` |
| Move Up | `I` |
| Shoot | `SPACE` |

---


## 🛠️ Built With

- Python
- Pygame

---

## 😂 Why I Made This

I was learning Pygame and wanted to make something random and fun instead of just following tutorials.

So I turned my friends into space enemies.

